cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "HORIZON: Real-Time Hantavirus Outbreak Surveillance Dataset"
message: >-
  If you use HORIZON data or software in your research, please cite it
  using the metadata in this file. Data is available under CC BY 4.0
  via the public API at https://hantavirus.software/api/v1/ and in bulk
  NDJSON format at https://hantavirus.software/api/v1/cases/bulk/ndjson
